(2, 'User Company Field & Where clause', 'user-company-field-where-clause', '<p>Hi,\nWhat is the best way to implement the following:\nI need for each user to have a company_id, and to simulate alike entry_by, so only records from the same company will appear in the results.\nThanks in advance,\nEduardo\nP.s. If you can implement this please let me know how much it will cost...\n</p>', 1, '2014-12-09 03:23:34', 252, 280, '0'),
(3, 'Number of records', 'number-of-records', '<p>How to set number of records in datasheet, from default 10 records</p>', 1, '2014-12-10 07:37:50', 212, 387, '0'),
(4, 'Date Format and downloads', 'date-format-and-downloads', '<p>1) How to display date in dd-mm-yyyy format. \n2) Downloading in excel, it download all the records, i want to download only records based on search or selected records, how can i do that.</p>', 1, '2014-12-10 07:39:54', 6424, 387, '0'),
(9, 'Managin session files', 'managin-session-files', '<p>Hello there. I manage all my projects with git and am using SximoBuilder for a team project on a shared repo. I have however noticed that files are created within the folder "protected/app/storage/sessions" and have chosen to add that folder to folder''s contents to the .gitignore file, so that those files do not fill the shared repository, but now I get my coleagues get errors when acessing the dev website.</p>\n\n<p>Is there anyway to effciently manage these files, so they won''t pile up and cause clutter in the server? Can i delete the old ones at least? Or does sximo need all of these files to function?</p>\n\n<p>Thank you.</p>', 1, '2015-01-05 18:35:24', 113, 419, '0'),
(7, 'Better Documentation?!', 'better-documentation', '<p>The documentation on setting up seems like it is only a fraction of what really needs to be done. I''m getting errors all of the place and it seems to be do to unfinished code. I see notes in most the files saying to set things up but can find no documentation on what to replace the code with.</p>', 1, '2014-12-26 23:13:41', 1399, 437, '0'),
(8, 'Bug when recovering forgotten password', 'bug-when-recovering-forgotten-password', '<p>Hi,</p>\n\n<p>I''ve found a bug when recovering a forgotten password. The link on the email to reset the password return an error on the $Q.\nOn sximobuilder.com occurs the same.</p>\n\n<p>**Error view**</p>\n\n<p>Open: ...\\protected\\app\\library\\SiteHelpers.php</p>\n\n<p>	public static function avatar( $width =75)\n	{<br />\n		$avatar = ''<img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar%20/''.md5(Session::get(''email'')).''" />'';<br />\n		$Q = DB::table("tb_users")-&gt;where("id",''='',Session::get(''uid''))-&gt;get();<br />\n                $row = $Q[0];<br />\n		$files =  ''./uploads/users/''.$row-&gt;avatar ;<br />\n		if($row-&gt;avatar !='''' ) 	</p>\n\n', 1, '2014-12-31 15:14:18', 159, 419, '0'),
(10, '2 Improvement', '2-improvement', '<p>Good day i´m here with 2 simple questions, </p>\n\n<p>1.  why is not an menu option to edit dashboard home using for example the wysiwyg editor? </p>\n\n<p>2.  is there an option to extend users , for example profile information  i means company and another some generated information</p>', 1, '2015-01-06 22:38:14', 1374, 462, '0'),
(11, 'Spanish translation', 'spanish-translation', '<p>Good Day</p>\n\n<p>i´m almost to finish Spanish translation and i like to share it, but there is some parts in the app that no have fields to translation, is possible to add it into translation module? and who i can send or share the spanish lang pack?</p>\n\n<p>for example :</p>\n\n<p>[Set of images without translation fields](http://imgur.com/a/iaGSG "Translation") </p>\n\n', 1, '2015-01-17 16:18:31', 98, 462, '0'),
(12, 'You got hacked :D or something similar.', 'you-got-hacked-d-or-something-similar', '<p>when you check the documentation is there an item with replacing content that is not official information. \nsaid this is me as a security concern about the project, please give us more knowledge about.</p>\n\n<p>http://sximobuilder.com/documentation/show/g5I9y-PCpS\nthen check Nufjkioi and Public Template :D</p>\n\n<p>\n[Imgur](http://i.imgur.com/jCmzzD1.png)</p>', 1, '2015-01-17 19:05:23', 202, 462, '0'),
(19, 'comboselect and filter', 'comboselect-and-filter', '<p>I''m trying to make the best use sximo builder.</p>\n\n<p>I''m using a table like this:</p>\n\n<p>MyTable:</p>\n\n<p>MyTableID int (11)<br />\nAnotherTableID int (11)<br />\n...</p>\n\n<p>in the table MyTable there is a reference ID of another table.</p>\n\n<p>Now I created the new table MyNewTable:</p>\n\n<p>MyNewTableID int (11)<br />\nMyTableID int (11)<br />\n...</p>\n\n<p>MyNewTable in there ''a reference to the MyTable table that I created earlier.</p>\n\n<p>I created a form with sximo builder that uses the table MyNewTable.\nIn the configuration form I set "form type" with "select option", "data type" with "database", I selected the table "MyNewTable".</p>\n\n<p>Now I would like to "display # 1", "# 2 display" and "display # 3" is not given the values of the ID, but the data of AnotherTable.</p>\n\n<p>I saw that the comboselect is created at runtime with an ajax call. According to the filter sximo builder returns the data in the table.</p>\n\n<p>How can I fix?</p>', 1, '2015-01-28 08:07:32', 936, 491, '0'),
(18, 'Relations many-to-mony', 'relations-many-to-mony', '<p>How create relations many-to-many?\nEg orders and products\nNeed add multi select item from other DB.</p>', 2, '2015-01-27 00:09:30', 194, 487, '0'),
(15, 'Sximo Ajax CRUD extension updates', 'sximo-ajax-crud-extension-updates', '<p>good morning, sorry for my orrible english.\nif I install the plugin ajax crud I necessarily have to rewrite the form all over again?\nwhen it is expected the update to version 3?</p>\n\n<p>reguards</p>', 1, '2015-01-24 08:17:19', 156, 491, '0'),
(17, 'How to do a Multi image upload', 'how-to-do-a-multi-image-upload', '<p>I need help on how to upload multiple images and store them in a certain unique directory, then just store comma separated file names in the database, similar to multiple checbox. </p>', 1, '2015-01-26 15:44:52', 274, 465, '0'),
(16, 'Module in MainSite', 'module-in-mainsite', '<p>Is it possible to show a module in frontside template?</p>', 1, '2015-01-26 12:39:53', 123, 491, '0'),
